data.title: Russell Crowe Answers the Web's Most Searched Questions
data.meta_description:
'Unhinged' star Russell Crowe answers the internet's most searched questions about himself. What is Russell Crowe doing right now? How old was Russell when he made 'Gladiator'? What band was Russell in? What color are his eyes? What did he win an Oscar for? Russell answers all these questions and more!
'Unhinged' releases July 10
